Package com.amplifyframework.storage

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    StorageCategoryBehavior
    Defines the behavior of the Storage category that clients will use.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    StorageCategory
    Defines the Client API consumed by the application.
    StorageCategoryConfiguration
    Strongly-typed configuration for Storage category that also contains configuration for individual plugins.
    StorageItem
    Used to store the data on each item in a storage.
    StoragePlugin<E>
    Abstract class that a plugin implementation of Hub Category would extend.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    StorageAccessLevel
    An enum of permission levels on storage operations.
    StorageChannelEventName
    An enumeration of the names of events relating the StorageCategory, that are published via HubCategory.publish(HubChannel, HubEvent) on the HubChannel.DATASTORE channel.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    StorageException
    Exception thrown by Storage category plugins.
